Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_mci::_bist_status

If clear BIST is desired, [CLEAR_BIST] must be written to 1 before [START_BIST] is written to 1 using a separate CSR write operation. [CLEAR_BIST] must not be changed after writing [START_BIST] to 1 until the BIST operation completes (indicated by [START_BIST] returning to 0) or operation is undefined.
